metadata.name: Sensitive Skin
metadata.description:
*We are architecture 
We are made of space 
Organic spaces that feel and mutate
Limits that hold and define
That split what is inside from what is not ourselves 
We let the light inside, we exchange our love
We try to embrace what we don't know
Fear is power and will close our windows
But the soul needs the air to survive its own wisdom*






Generative animation created with custom Python scripts using Blender and Sverchok.


Victor Doval. 2023
